set_protector
Discworld combat help
set_protector

Name
.SI 5
set_protector - Sets the protector object.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_protector(object ob);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
The protector object is used when the person is being attacked.  The
object has an 80% chance of taking the attack instead of the creature
being attacked.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
attack, combat, query_protector
.EP
